          <sec id="Metronidazole.Comment">
            <title>Comment</title>
            <p>The serum enzyme elevations were compatible with mild metronidazole hepatotoxicity, given the short latency period and rapid recovery after stopping. The rapid onset and rapid recovery after high doses of intravenous metronidazole suggest direct hepatic injury. However, idiosyncratic cases are also marked by short latency period and rechallenge, even with oral metronidazole should be avoided.</p>
          </sec>
